Title: How to discover THE Portugal
DateModified: '2019-02-18'
DatePublished: '2019-02-18'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/how-to-discover-the-portugal
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Sylvain Delor
AuthorCountry: Chile
Text: "Come and share with me my way to discover my Portugal!\nI'll take you with\
  \ me in the douro valley where is situated the vineyard to product the Porto wine.\
  \ There is a railway line which is one the most beautifull line of Europe. \nI'll\
  \ take you in some good restaurants,realy ship and realy delicious.\nI'll teach\
  \ you my favorites beaches which are unknown by the tourisme.\nCome and share a\
  \ good meal of fresh  fish with the local fisherman.\nWe'll meet a lot of local\
  \ people how have good story to tell us."
